(This file, NEWS, lists new features and enhancements. See CHANGES for fixes.)

1.0.4 2023-06-11

  * RecSplit has now a bitCount() function reporting the space used,
    including the structure itself. Also the printed information has been
    updated to contain the space used by the structure. Thanks to 
    Hans-Peter Lehmann reporting this issue.

1.0.1 2019-05-18

  * RecSplit is now thread-safe.

1.0.0 2019-05-26

  * First release.
